n":"vertical-bottom horizontal-left","overlay_opacity":0,"focal_point":"center center"}}},"block_order":["1653021974609b96cc-0","1653021974609b96cc-1","61c57576-ede4-4482-ab91-b6464a8300fe","1a1a75af-eb24-49d4-b24d-113db6df6b4d","0354dc7a-e125-4a65-b867-b32352995e4d"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":true,"desktop_size":0,"mobile_size":0,"style":"arrows","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":7}},"16530219983767b8f3":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"16530219988be631f3-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Get, Set, Refer!"}},"16530219988be631f3-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>It's a good day to REFER our products to your <strong>#SkincareSquad <\/strong>as<br\/><br\/>* You shall receive <strong>Rs. 250 CAPital<\/strong> in your CAPBank.<br\/><br\/>* Your friends will enjoy <strong>50% OFF <\/strong>sitewide.<\/p>"}},"9a4e448b-5a32-4481-a6f8-fe46cdada83f":{"type":"button","settings":{"link":"","link_text":"Refer Now"}}},"block_order":["16530219988be631f3-0","16530219988be631f3-1","9a4e448b-5a32-4481-a6f8-fe46cdada83f"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"align_text":"center","narrow_column":true,"color_scheme":"3","divider":false}},"1653022071095ae3f7":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"1653022071f581370f-0":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Why do skin junkies prefer ceramide-based products?","text":"<p>Ceramides are lipids (fats) that are found in our skin naturally. They make up about 50% of the skin's top layer (epidermis), thus being an important component of the skin.<\/p><p>And as we age, their production decreases which leads to multiple skin woes such as dryness and signs of ageing. <\/p><p>Ceramides are the ultimate daddy of skincare ingredients because they...<\/p><p>Help trap the moisture inside the skin<\/p><p>Help strengthen the barrier of the skin<\/p><p>Improve the overall appearance of the skin<\/p><p>Fight signs of ageing such as fine lines, wrinkles, age spots, etc.<\/p><p>That's not all, they are the only ingredient that starts to work in about 10 minutes!<\/p><p>They have gained a lot of interest in the skincare world because of all the amazing benefits of ceramides for the skin. Trust us- if you want your skin to thank you later, then include ceramides-based products in your skincare regimen!<\/p>"}},"1653022071f581370f-1":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are ceramides good for oily skin?","text":"<p>Another notable benefit of ceramides are that they are suitable for all skin types. So yes, ceramides are great for oily skin as well.<\/p><p>Understand it this way- ceramides are found naturally in the skin, thus they are 'skin-identical' to all skin types!<\/p>"}},"a35e7409-f2b3-4cf1-ac8f-426efa6335b2":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are ceramides safe for skin?","text":"<p>Ceramides are found in the top layer of the skin. In fact, it comprises almost 50% of the skin's top layer (yup, that's a lot of ceramides!). They help strengthen the barrier of the skin, among other skincare benefits. <\/p><p>To sum it up, ceramides are safe as they have nothing but great news for our skin!<\/p><p>Ceramides act like 'cement for the skin'- holding the skin cells together and keeping the skin looking young and so fine! They also help trap in the moisture, thus keeping the skin moisturized for longer hours.<\/p>"}},"2e84b87c-1f40-416e-9a94-7cd19fb34ed5":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Do all products of Chemist at Play have ceramides?","text":"<p>Hell yes!<\/p><p>Chemist at Play is India's first ceramides-based skincare brand and all our products, be it skin or body care, are infused with the goodness of essential ceramides. Since we love animals (we are also a cruelty-free brand), we took the phytoceramides (plant-based ceramides) route.<\/p>"}},"71682a9b-b2d8-45b2-8f85-1682e54b5118":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Where do ceramides come from?","text":"<p>Ceramides are found naturally in our skin's top layer. But, you can also derive them from animals as well as plants.<\/p><p>The benefits of ceramides are aplenty; improves the overall appearance of the skin, strengthens the skin barrier, are loaded with anti-aging properties, etc.<\/p><p>And as we age, their production decreases. <\/p><p>Thus, using ceramides-infused skincare products should be your ultimate skincare goal!<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["1653022071f581370f-0","1653022071f581370f-1","a35e7409-f2b3-4cf1-ac8f-426efa6335b2","2e84b87c-1f40-416e-9a94-7cd19fb34ed5","71682a9b-b2d8-45b2-8f85-1682e54b5118"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"India's First Ceramides-Based Skincare Brand"}}},"order":["main","1653021743ec99e173","16572687323756e433","1653021750f59e8592","1653021838ee6246cd","1653021843c07eb01f","16530218506fb15eec","1653021859795d33aa","16530218998069e722","1653021974bdb7f8aa","16530219983767b8f3","1653022071095ae3f7"]}